title: CDCS Costa Del Sol Nairi's
text:
Costa Del Sol Nairi's was a <a href="Belize">Belize</a>an <a href="Association%20football">football</a> team that formerly competed in the Belize Premier Football League (BPFL) of the <a href="Football%20Federation%20of%20Belize">Football Federation of Belize</a>.
The team was based in <a href="San%20Pedro%20Town">San Pedro Town</a>. Their home stadium was <a href="Ambergris%20Stadium">Ambergris Stadium</a>.
